title: Redshift UCTM: System Statistics
agents: special
catalog: os/networking
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors system statistics from Redshift Networks UCTM devices
 including memory usage, CPU utilization, and license information.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Redshift Networks UCTM}.

 The check reports memory usage with metrics for used and total memory,
 as well as percentage utilization. It transitions to {WARN} at 90% memory
 usage and {CRIT} at 95%.

 CPU usage is monitored with a {WARN} threshold at 80% and {CRIT} at 90%.

 License expiration information is displayed when available.

discovery:
 One service is created if system statistics data is available from the device.

item:
 None
